%% LM Evaluation Harness - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as LMES Operator<br/>(TrustyAI)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LMES as LMES Job Container<br/>Python 3.11
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Model as Model Inference<br/>Endpoint<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Registry as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>HTTP/HTTPS

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job + ConfigMap (job.json)<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>LMES: Mount ConfigMap at /meta/job.json

    LMES->>EvalHub: POST status: INITIALIZING<br/>TLS (configurable) / Bearer Token

    opt Online Mode (not disconnected)
        LMES->>HFHub: Download tokenizer/datasets<br/>TLS 1.2+ / HF_TOKEN (optional)
        HFHub-->>LMES: Tokenizer + dataset artifacts
    end

    LMES->>EvalHub: POST status: LOADING_DATA<br/>TLS (configurable) / Bearer Token

    loop For each evaluation task/benchmark
        LMES->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>TLS (configurable) / Bearer Token (API Key)
        Model-->>LMES: Completion responses
    end

    LMES->>EvalHub: POST status: RUNNING_EVALUATION<br/>TLS (configurable) / Bearer Token

    Note over LMES: Compute metrics<br/>(54 offline modules)

    LMES->>EvalHub: POST status: POST_PROCESSING<br/>TLS (configurable) / Bearer Token

    LMES->>LMES: Write results JSON to<br/>/opt/app-root/src/output/
    LMES->>LMES: Create OCI layout at<br/>/tmp/oci-layout (olot)
    LMES->>Registry: skopeo push OCI artifact<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Docker auth

    LMES->>EvalHub: POST status: PERSISTING_ARTIFACTS<br/>+ final results<br/>TLS (configurable) / Bearer Token

    opt MLflow enabled
        LMES->>MLflow: Log metrics + parameters<br/>TLS (configurable) / Token
    end
